data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!!   Welcome to your dream home at 3331 Metro Way, Snellville, Georgia 30039-7718! Nestled in a serene and immaculate neighborhood on a charming cul-de-sac, this property offers the perfect blend of tranquility and sophistication.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a well-designed interior that maximizes space and comfort. With 3 bedrooms, each boasting ample closet space, and 2 full bathrooms, this residence is ideal for those who appreciate both style and functionality.    The spacious living room provides an inviting atmosphere for relaxation, while the separate dining room offers a delightful setting for family gatherings and entertaining guests. The kitchen is a true culinary haven, featuring pristine white cabinets, elegant black granite countertops, and a stunning backsplash design that adds a touch of contemporary flair. The breakfast area is perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or casual meals.    The master bedroom, located in a private wing of the property, is a retreat in itself. It boasts generous proportions, an en-suite bathroom for added convenience, and an amazing walk-in closet that caters to your storage needs. Natural light floods the space, creating an airy and uplifting ambiance.    Practical amenities such as a water heater, and a heating and cooling unit in optimal condition ensure that your everyday living experience is seamless and comfortable.    Step outside to discover a backyard oasis – a spacious and level area enclosed by a wooden fence, providing both privacy and a picturesque view. Whether you envision cozy evenings under the stars or outdoor activities, this backyard is a canvas for your imagination.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your own – a place where every detail has been carefully well-maintained to keep a harmonious blend of style, comfort, and functionality. Your dream home awaits at 3331 Metro Way!
